---
title: Loaded Chipotle Pulled Chicken Rice Bowl with Cheddar, Pickled Onion and Salad
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Loaded Chipotle Pulled Chicken Rice Bowl in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R15_W16_UK_HVP19065-4_MAIN_low-15217611.jpg
